token_info.description: This figurine of OX depicts the Minoriea enthroned on her mother OX’s royal lap. A statue of the RAM ancestor worn as a crown. Digital sculpture by Auriea Harvey.  AR on mobile. Unlockable content: the artist will install the sculpture on the web server or metaverse of the owner’s choice. Contact bitforms gallery for details - info@bitforms.art
